      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride at a reasonable price? This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it's fully drivable and gets you where you need to go! You'll notice some visible wear on the exterior and interior, and there may be a few minor mechanical items worth attention down the road, but the core systems are functional. A great option for a practical buyer who wants solid transportation without the premium price tag!",
